{"tid":867010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖北男屎坑撈魚 卡住隻手call消防求救","createTime":"2018-10-18T10:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T14:40:50.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4b49d3af7903d728566038faab5ba962a3ee06f4","tid":867010,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181018/_2018101812363838025.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181018%2F_2018101812363838025.jpg&h=aae29035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">男子厠所撈魚，不料卡住手臂，整個人起不來。（網圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n上周六（13日）晚上，湖北襄陽發生了一件令人哭笑不得的事情。一名男子看街市的魚既便宜又新鮮，便買了幾條回家，心想這幾天能夠吃上一頓好的了。該名男子回到家中，跑到廁所，便開始清理鮮魚，清完一條還有一條，眼看這是最後一條了，男子想着終於能清理完了，馬上就能吃好的了。誰知，這條魚太新鮮太活潑，就這麼挺身一躍，跳進了廁所裏！<br />\n<br />\n男子眼看魚跳進廁所裏，即時撲到廁所，伸手入廁所抓魚，豈料魚沒抓到，整個胳膊都塞進廁所的下水管道，被卡住了！男子掙扎了半天也沒拔出自己的胳膊，躺在厠所急得滿頭大汗。<br />\n<br />\n最後，男子沒辦法，只能報警找來消防員幫忙，幸虧手機在旁，不然喊救命也不知有沒有人回應！救援人員趕來後，慢慢的用工具將廁所敲碎，該男子才能得救，幸好該男子在事件中並沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181018/_2018101812363936891.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181018%2F_2018101812363936891.jpg&h=30cab265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/843343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F843343&d=48Q0sfUiPCFtPlwj4gyWohv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8261f16a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F843343&h=1f64214e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/843343</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4c42b0da6850f8793132afe86cd7ae026c8012","tid":867010,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 咁大個人學人玩屎？！"},{"pid":"3679ab8982ca278ba97722a668dbc771c4bd38cc","tid":867010,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"da4c42b0da6850f8793132afe86cd7ae026c8012","tid":867010,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 咁大個人學人玩屎？！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"佢竟然抱住<br />\n「可以撈番條屎魚食」<br />\n呢個諗法"},{"pid":"7bcf9220e87c840f2402d9a02f5bf5b07c8e44d1","tid":867010,"uid":18517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836bc8ce100d7c9d1d65e90561ac4c08ed3eb54c","tid":867010,"uid":188178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"踎廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab53bc94d4d9267e278c7dd386d9b949e5800d6","tid":867010,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3679ab8982ca278ba97722a668dbc771c4bd38cc","tid":867010,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"da4c42b0da6850f8793132afe86cd7ae026c8012","tid":867010,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 咁大個人學人玩屎？！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"佢竟然抱住<br />\n「可以撈番條屎魚食」<br />\n呢個諗法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，佢地一定係賣返出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f271c23ee03d69c88d2db83dc141df2a5c1d7288","tid":867010,"uid":168525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3679ab8982ca278ba97722a668dbc771c4bd38cc","tid":867010,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"da4c42b0da6850f8793132afe86cd7ae026c8012","tid":867010,"uid":96743,"like":